  "detailed_description": "高三的生活，对于学生来说是人生中最重要的时刻，刚刚踏入高三的主人公晨约，对未来感到了迷茫，对高考之后的志愿，以及今后的职业规划有着非常模糊的感觉。就在他迎接着为止的将来的时候，有一位许久不见的朋友闯入了他的生活中。<br>《真愿交错》是一部讲述日常学校生活的日常游戏，游戏内有诸多选项分支可以选择，每次的分支都将会决定最后交往不同的角色，要谨慎选择哦<br>\"True Wish Interlace\" is a daily game that tells the story of school life. There are many options and branches to choose from in the game, and each branch will determine the final interaction with different characters. Be careful when choosing<br><br>人物简介<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001160/extras/b49b806dbc49ae1bd5b70cddf5e72e6e.avif?t=1720499562\" width=620 height=876 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001160/extras/b765153d2d2105dd3ce329a37c9e76d0.avif?t=1720499562\" width=620 height=877 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001160/extras/f4f61c2e76fd67d04050bc02b96c7d12.avif?t=1720499562\" width=620 height=877 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001160/extras/861e83fe6ead2db3a654c1ede2456cce.avif?t=1720499562\" width=620 height=876 /></span><br><br>人物立绘设计：天黎<br>表情差分：暴走瞌睡虫<br>cg设计：耳朵酱，yuyuvn，六柰，kiwiiii<br>背景设计：背景専門店みにくる<br>图标设计：汤饺<br><br>对游戏有何意见或是问题，都可以通过邮件方式来联系我们<br><a href=\"mailto:邮箱地址：3421349607@qq.com\">邮箱地址：3421349607@qq.com</a><br>那么，再次感谢大家游玩，祝大家玩的开心",
